Vodafone Hires Joseph as Director of Payments, Telegraph Says

-- B y   T o n y   C .   D r e i b u s
-- 
2011-12-11T09:16:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-11/vodafone-hires-joseph-as-director-of-payments-telegraph-says.html
Vodafone Group Plc has hired Michael Joseph, the former CEO of Kenyan mobile operator  Safaricom Ltd. ,
as director of global payments, the Sunday Telegraph reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony C. Dreibus in  London  at 
 tdreibus@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
